        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Resident Education Deferred Interest Act or the REDI Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes student loan borrowers eligible for interest-free deferment on loans under the William D. Ford Federal Direct Loan Program if the borrowers are serving in medical or dental internships or residency programs.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
